Subject: Migrating data
Description:
We are migratingto a new server that is fully updated as teh current server we are having issues of where it does reboot after an update
I would like to export just the data nothing else, so i chose the system backup and selected Database Content, Application Sources.
System backup hangs at 99% and it goes no further.
Is there any other way of extracting just the data, and importing the data onto the new server?
Solution_Comment__c: Solved by helping the customer with the System backup V2 for the migration.
